block content
    .container1
      nav.navbar
        ul
          li.nav-item
            a(href="/") Home
          li.nav-item
            a(href="/about") About
          li.nav-item
            a(href="/services") Services
          li.nav-item
            a(href="/contact") Contact
        h1.cont1h1 TRANSFORM YOUR BODY. START WORKING OUT NOW

        p.cont1p
        | Build muscles and stengthen your body and mind with our expert trainers and state-of-the-art equipment.Join us today and take the first step towards a healthier, fitter you!

    .box
      h3.boxh1 REACH YOUR FITNESS GOALS BY DOING THESE EXERCISES

      .line

      .box1
        .box11
          img(src="../static/images/cardio.webp", alt="Gym Image 1")

        .box12
          h3 Cardio for you endurance and cardiovascular health
          p
            | Cardio is an important form of exercise that improves overall health and fitness.
            | It strengthens the heart, increases lung capacity, and improves blood circulation.
            | Regular cardio helps burn calories, manage body weight, and reduce the risk of diseases like diabetes and heart problems.
            | It also improves stamina, energy levels, and sleep quality.

      .line

      .box2
        .box21
          img(src="../static/images/strength training.jpg", alt="Gym Image 1")

        .box22
          h3 Strength Training for Building Muscle and Bone Density and strengthen your body
          p Strength training is an effective exercise method that builds muscle strength, improves body shape, and increases physical power. It helps strengthen bones, boost metabolism, support fat loss, and improve posture. Regular strength training enhances daily performance, reduces injury risk, and increases confidence. It also helps maintain overall fitness and a healthier lifestyle.
            

      .line

      .box3
        .box31
          img(src="../static/images/stretching.avif", alt="Gym Image 1")

        .box32
          h3 Stretching for relax your muscles and improve flexibility over time

          p Stretching is an important exercise that improves flexibility, mobility, and muscle relaxation. It helps increase range of motion, reduce muscle stiffness, and improve posture. Regular stretching supports better movement, decreases the risk of injuries, and helps recovery after workouts. It also promotes relaxation, reduces stress, and keeps the body active and balanced.

      .line

